{"tid":2439508,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登有愛]請大家叫身邊人登記器官捐贈","createTime":"2021-03-09T09:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T12:39:53.000Z","uid":36419,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40781afa4967eb4cad9af55a33e2b9a05c2201f1","tid":2439508,"uid":36419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:57:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟媽媽幾年前已發現患上好罕有嘅肺病，最近病情急轉直下，只淨返肺移植可以幫到佢。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能好短期內已經唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以小弟係到呼籲大家叫埋自己身邊嘅人登記器官捐贈，死左都可以幫到有需要嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係家人有事先明白要等換器官果種無力感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我幫唔到我媽媽唯有自己都登記希望可以幫到其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n登記傳送門:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.codr.gov.hk/codr/CInternet.jsf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.codr.gov.hk%2Fcodr%2FCInternet.jsf&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy6xOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=639ae608\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.codr.gov.hk/codr/CInternet.jsf</a>"},{"pid":"54f5a49400a10dd8cb78d5e84565387b386ac9e3","tid":2439508,"uid":197750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"希望伯母早日康服！"},{"pid":"e6815ca9870f1a12d771f057181024664e3d7c37","tid":2439508,"uid":36419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54f5a49400a10dd8cb78d5e84565387b386ac9e3","tid":2439508,"uid":197750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"希望伯母早日康服！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728ec6fb3e664da65d381c593032deaf83792fb2","tid":2439508,"uid":11020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"幫樓主推